Symbol.Script_3D:
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000
PEN gs_cont_pen MATERIAL col_mat IF gs_shadow=0 THEN SHADOW off ELSE SHADOW on ENDIF
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 THEN end
!---------Cutplanes modz = zzyzx IF bCutPlanes Then
wsds = sqr(sectDepth^2 + sectWidth^2)
!!!-------------------- Top Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds/2
Rotz gs_cutdir_top addz zzyzx rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang1_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang2_bot)* wsds /2
del 3 Endif
!!!-------------------- Bottom Cutting If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS Then modz = modz+tan(60)* wsds /2
Rotz gs_cutdir_but rotx 90
cutpoly 5, -wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2,-tan(60)* wsds /2, wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang3_bot)* wsds /2, 0,0, -wsds/2, tan(gs_cutang4_bot)* wsds /2
del 2 addz -tan(60)*wsds/2 Endif Endif !---------Cutplanes
RRadius=sectThick*2
IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 THEN PRISM_ 10,modz, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,15, sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,15, sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2,15, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2,15, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,-1, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectThick-sectDepth/2,15, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectThick-sectDepth/2,15, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectDepth/2-sectThick,15, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2-sectThick,15, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectThick-sectDepth/2,-1 ENDIF IF gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 THEN RESOL gs_resol PRISM_ 28,modz, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2-RRadius,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2,79, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,79, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2,-1,
-sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectDepth/2-RRadius,79, sectWidth/2-RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-sectThick,79, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2+sectThick,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,79, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,979, 0,90,4079, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,-1 ENDIF
!---------Cutplanes IF bCutPlanes Then If ABS(gs_cutang1_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang2_bot) > EPS Then cutend
If ABS(gs_cutang3_bot) > EPS OR ABS(gs_cutang4_bot) > EPS Then del 1 cutend Endif Endif !---------Cutplanes
unID=1 HOTSPOT 0,0,0,unID,ZZYZX,1+256 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,-1,unID,ZZYZX,3 : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT 0,0,ZZYZX,unID,ZZYZX,2 : unID=unID+1
!---------Bottom Hotspots cutAngleHSBot1 = gs_cutang3_bot cutAngleHSBot3 = gs_cutang4_bot
if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HPBotx = sectDepth cutAngleHSBot2 = gs_cutang4_bot cutAngleHSBot4 = gs_cutang3_bot else HPBotx = sectWidth cutAngleHSBot2 = gs_cutang3_bot cutAngleHSBot4 = gs_cutang4_bot endif
rotx 90
HOTSPOT sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot2)* HPBotx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot3)* HPBotx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot4)* HPBotx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHSBot1)* HPBotx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 1
!---------Top Hotspots cutAngleHS1 = gs_cutang1_bot cutAngleHS3 = gs_cutang2_bot
if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_X then HPx = sectDepth cutAngleHS2 = gs_cutang2_bot cutAngleHS4 = gs_cutang1_bot else HPx = sectWidth cutAngleHS2 = gs_cutang1_bot cutAngleHS4 = gs_cutang2_bot endif
addz zzyzx rotx 90
HOTSPOT sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS2)* HPx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS3)* HPx/2, sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT -sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS4)* HPx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 HOTSPOT sectWidth/2, bCutPlanes*tan(cutAngleHS1)* HPx/2, -sectDepth/2, unID : unID = unID+1 del 2
end
Symbol.Script_2D:
sectWidth=sectWidth/1000 sectDepth=sectDepth/1000 sectThick=sectThick/1000
PEN gs_cont_pen FILL gs_fill_type
unID=1 hLineID = 1000
HOTSPOT2 0, 0,unID : unID=unID+1
IF axis=1 AND only_axis=0 OR axis=0 THEN
RRadius=sectThick*2
if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 then POLY2_b 10, 1+2+4+32, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2,1+32, -sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2,1+32, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,-1, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectThick-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectThick-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectDepth/2-sectThick,1+32, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2-sectThick,1+32, sectThick-sectWidth/2,sectThick-sectDepth/2,-1
gosub "hotlines2D"
ENDIF IF gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 THEN POLY2_b 28, 1+2+4+32, gs_fill_pen, gs_back_pen, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2-RRadius,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2,1+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,1+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2,-1,
-sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, sectWidth/2-sectThick,sectDepth/2-RRadius,1+32, sectWidth/2-RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-sectThick,1+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,sectDepth/2-RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2+sectThick,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,1+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+RRadius,901+32, 0,90,4001+32, -sectWidth/2+RRadius,-sectDepth/2+sectThick,-1
gosub "hotlines2D"
ENDIF
HOTSPOT2 -a/2, -b/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, -b/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a/2, b/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -a/2, b/2,unID : unID=unID+1
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN
HOTSPOT2 -a/2+sectThick, -b/2+sectThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a/2-sectThick, -b/2+sectThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 a/2-sectThick, b/2-sectThick,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 -a/2+sectThick, b/2-sectThick,unID : unID=unID+1
ENDIF
ENDIF
unID=100 IF (axis=1) THEN PEN axis_line_pen LINE_TYPE axis_line_type
LINE2 -axis_XDim, 0, axis_XDim,0 LINE2 0, -axis_YDim, 0,axis_YDim
FOR k1=1 TO 2 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 1+128: unID=unID+1 !!! Axis X Dim. from Origo HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 axis_XDim, 0, unID, axis_XDim, 2: unID=unID+1 ROT2 180 NEXT k1 DEL 2
FOR k2=1 TO 2 ROT2 90 HOTSPOT2 0, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 1+128: unID=unID+1 !!! Axis Y Dim. from Origo HOTSPOT2 -1, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 3: unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 axis_YDim, 0, unID, axis_YDim, 2: unID=unID+1 DEL 1 ROT2 180 NEXT k2 DEL 2
IF gs_ShowMoreHtps2D=1 THEN HOTSPOT2 -sectWidth/2, 0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 sectWidth/2, 0,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, -sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1 HOTSPOT2 0, sectDepth/2,unID : unID=unID+1 ENDIF
ENDIF
end
"hotlines2D": HOTLINE2 -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2, hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 HOTLINE2 sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2, hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 HOTLINE2 -sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2,sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2, hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 HOTLINE2 -sectWidth/2,-sectDepth/2,-sectWidth/2,sectDepth/2, hLineID : hLineID = hLineID + 1 return

EPS = 0.0001 iStructureCode = 40 !CODECOL_SHSCOLD
! iCutModeColBottom, iCutModeColTop CUTMODE_ALONG_X = 1 CUTMODE_ALONG_Y = 2
Symbol.Script_VL:
! -------------------------------------------------------------------------------- ! hide All Parameters list ! --------------------------------------------------------------------------------
hideparameter all "A", "B", "ZZYZX"
sor = 80 ! Number of Lines file_dependence "SHS Cold-Formed(14).txt"
prof = 18 ! Number of Sections
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "Profile" or siz_mtr[1] = "" then
dim vekt[18] dim namevekt[18]
for i = 1 to 18 vekt[i] = 0 namevekt[i] = "" next i
szelv=open("text", "SHS Cold-Formed(14).txt", "separator='\t', mode=ro, Library")
j=1 for i=2 to sor+1 v1 = 0 v2 = 0 n=input(szelv, i, 2, v1, v2) nincs = 1 for k=1 to prof if vekt[k]=v2 then nincs = 0 endif next k if nincs = 1 then vekt[j] = v2 namevekt[j] = v1 j=j+1 endif next i
namevekt[prof] = `СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЙ`
siz_mtr = namevekt
parameters siz_mtr = siz_mtr
for i=1 to prof if namevekt[i]=Profile then parameters sectDepth=vekt[i] sectDepth=vekt[i] endif next i
close szelv endif call "FM_types" parameters all
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=28 if gs_fill_pen=0 then PARAMETERS gs_fill_pen=19 if axis_line_pen=0 then PARAMETERS axis_line_pen=68
values "gs_resol" RANGE [3,) if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 then lock "gs_resol"
values "sectThick" range (0, min(sectWidth/2, sectDepth/2))
dim stDetLevel3d[3] stDetLevel3d[1] = `Простой` stDetLevel3d[2] = `Детальный` stDetLevel3d[3] = `Откл.`
values "gs_detlevel_3D" stDetLevel3d values "gs_detlevel_3D_m" 1, 2, 0
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_3D" then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[2] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 if gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[3] then gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 parameters gs_detlevel_3D_m = gs_detlevel_3D_m else gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[1] if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[2] if gs_detlevel_3D_m = 0 then gs_detlevel_3D = stDetLevel3d[3] parameters gs_detlevel_3D = gs_detlevel_3D endif dim stDetLevel2d[2] stDetLevel2d[1] = `Простой` stDetLevel2d[2] = `Детальный`
values "gs_detlevel_2D" stDetLevel2d values "gs_detlevel_2D_m" 1, 2
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "gs_detlevel_2D" then gs_detlevel_2D_m = 1 if gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[2] then gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 parameters gs_detlevel_2D_m = gs_detlevel_2D_m else gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[1] if gs_detlevel_2D_m = 2 then gs_detlevel_2D = stDetLevel2d[2] parameters gs_detlevel_2D = gs_detlevel_2D endif
!---------Cutplanes dim stCutModeColValues[2] stCutModeColValues[1] = `Вдоль оси X` stCutModeColValues[2] = `Вдоль оси Y`
values "stCutModeColTop" stCutModeColValues values "iCutModeColTop" CUTMODE_ALONG_X, CUTMODE_ALONG_Y
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stCutModeColTop" then iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_X if stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[2] then iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y parameters iCutModeColTop = iCutModeColTop else stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[1] if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColValues[2] parameters stCutModeColTop = stCutModeColTop endif
values "stCutModeColBottom" stCutModeColValues values "iCutModeColBottom" CUTMODE_ALONG_X, CUTMODE_ALONG_Y
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "stCutModeColBottom" then iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_X if stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[2] then iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y parameters iCutModeColBottom = iCutModeColBottom else stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[1] if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColValues[2] parameters stCutModeColBottom = stCutModeColBottom endif values "gs_cutdir_top" RANGE [-90,90] values "gs_cutdir_but" RANGE [-90,90] values "gs_cutang1_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang2_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang3_bot" RANGE [-60,60] values "gs_cutang4_bot" RANGE [-60,60]
if iCutModeColTop = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then gs_cutdir_top = 0.00 parameters gs_cutdir_top = gs_cutdir_top else gs_cutdir_top = 90.00 parameters gs_cutdir_top = gs_cutdir_top endif
if iCutModeColBottom = CUTMODE_ALONG_Y then gs_cutdir_but = 0.00 parameters gs_cutdir_but = gs_cutdir_but else gs_cutdir_but = 90.00 parameters gs_cutdir_but = gs_cutdir_but endif
if NOT(bCutPlanes) then hideparameter "stCutModeColTop", "iCutModeColTop", "stCutModeColBottom", "iCutModeColBottom", "gs_cutang1_bot","gs_cutang2_bot","gs_cutang3_bot","gs_cutang4_bot" Lock "stCutModeColTop", "iCutModeColTop", "stCutModeColBottom", "iCutModeColBottom", "gs_cutang1_bot","gs_cutang2_bot","gs_cutang3_bot","gs_cutang4_bot" endif
! --- Cutplanes ----------------------------------------------------------------
values "Profile" siz_mtr
if Profile<>`СПЕЦИАЛЬНЫЙ` then lock "sectWidth" lock "sectDepth"
if Profile <> lastProfile then
lastProfile = Profile parameters lastProfile = Profile
szelv=open("TEXT", "SHS Cold-Formed(14).txt", "SEPARATOR='\t', mode=ro, Library") for i=2 to sor+1 n=input(szelv, i, 3, ker) if sectDepth=ker then n=input(szelv, i, 4, osectThick) put osectThick endif next i
values "sectThick" use(NSP)
szelv=open("text", "SHS Cold-Formed(14).txt", "separator='\t', mode=ro, Library")
for i=2 to sor+1 n=input(szelv, i, 3, ker1, ker2) if (sectDepth=ker1) and (sectThick=ker2) then n=input(szelv, i, 5, omassPerMeter, osectArea, odpt, osecondMoment, ogyrationRad, oelastMod, oplastMod) next i close szelv
parameters sectWidth=sectDepth parameters a=sectDepth/1000 parameters b=sectDepth/1000 parameters massPerMeter=omassPerMeter parameters secondMoment=osecondMoment parameters gyrationRad=ogyrationRad parameters elastMod=oelastMod parameters plastMod=oplastMod parameters sectArea=osectArea endif
lock "sectWidth" lock "a" lock "b" lock "massPerMeter" lock "secondMoment" lock "gyrationRad" lock "elastMod" lock "plastMod" lock "sectArea" else values "sectDepth" range (0.001, )
parameters massPerMeter=massPerMeter parameters sectWidth=sectDepth lock "sectWidth" parameters sectDepth=sectDepth parameters sectThick=sectThick parameters secondMoment=secondMoment parameters gyrationRad=gyrationRad parameters elastMod=elastMod parameters plastMod=plastMod parameters sectArea=sectArea if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "sectDepth" then A = sectDepth/1000 parameters A = A B = sectDepth/1000 parameters B = B else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "A" then sectDepth = A*1000 parameters sectDepth = sectDepth B = A parameters B = B else if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME = "B" then parameters sectDepth = B*1000 sectDepth = d A = B parameters A = A endif endif endif endif
massSum=massPerMeter*ZZYZX parameters massSum=massSum lock "massSum"
if GLOB_MODPAR_NAME="Profile" then parameters axis_XDim=a/2+0.05 axis_XDim=a/2+0.05
parameters axis_YDim=b/2+0.05 axis_YDim=b/2+0.05 endif
if not(axis) then lock "only_axis", "axis_line_type", "axis_line_pen", "axis_XDim", "axis_YDim" endif if axis and only_axis then lock "gs_cont_pen", "gs_fill_type", "gs_fill_pen", "gs_back_pen", "gs_detlevel_2D", "gs_ShowMoreHtps2D" endif
parameters ac_bottomlevel = 0 parameters ac_toplevel = ZZYZX
